Introducing two new SayHi Beta experiences: SayHi Conversation and SayHi Image! SayHi Conversation is a new hands free translation conversation experience. SayHi Image lets you take a photo or upload an image containing text and translates it instantly. Install and try both new experiences today! Ready for iPhone X

Faster translations: We ve been working hard to make your translations are even faster! Swipe to delete: Swipe to the left on individual phrases to delete them without clearing your entire conversation. Tap to edit: Now you can edit What you said or your translations. Your edits will improve the quality of our service in the future! Toggle to type: If you would like to primarily type text into the app open the language list at the bottom of the conversation view then tap the toggle to always type. Improved localizations: We ve improved localizations throughout the app. Thank you for all of your feedback! New look: We gave SayHi a makeover with a simple modern look. Hold to type: Hold the mic button to quickly bring up a keyboard. New navigation: Tap the menu button to access settings and more. Accessible: Voiceover is once again fully supported as well as Dynamic Type and improved navigation for accessiblity.

If you missed it in the last update SayHi now runs natively on iPads! By popular demand: Translation sharing options! Tap the drawer button next to any translation and you will find a new button to Email Message Tweet Text or Copy your translation. Further improvements for VoiceOver accessibility users.. Bug fixes and other improvements
New iPad Support! SayHi Translate is finally a Universal App! Looks great on the new iPad! We have more improvements planned so stay tuned!

SayHi no longer requires an account! If you ever downloaded it in the past you can start using it right now for free! Enjoy! Added button to rate the app on the App Store The more ratings we get the better we can make our product! Added button to tweet about SayHi Translate requires iOS 5.0 or later and a configured twitter account . Let us know what you think we re always looking to make improvements. Improved accessibility user experience. More improvements to come!

We ve dropped our pricing! Instead of monthly pricing SayHi Translate is now one price forever!!!! Added support for Russian and Brazilian Portuguese We ve got a new look! Added automatic introduction tutorials to ease use of the app with new users. Tap the new question mark button to access them. Added speech detection notification sounds. Toggle them on or off in the settings.
Added support for: Danish Portuguese Portugal Polish

Added a toggle in settings to control auto detection of the end of speech. This is defaulted to off to minimize input errors. Toggle this on to allow the app to detect when you are done talking like Siri Updated speech systems Nationality flags for language list Alphabetized language list Enhanced management of language management allowing us to more quickly add languages in future Many other minor enhancements corrections and performance improvements

Fixed a bug that could cause the app to hang with a done button. Fixed a bug that could cause some text to disappear from the conversation view when scrolling. Input buttons show a disabled state when they are unavailable. Minor performance enhancements. Smaller file size.

Support for 11 new languages and dialects! English United Kingdom English Australia Spanish United States Spanish Mexico French Canada Mandarin Taiwan Cantonese Korean Dutch Norwegian Swedish Switched to all streaming voices. This means the app is 1 100th the size it used to be even with all the new languages! Added ability to email support directly from the app. Various speed improvements and bug fixes.

New application icon to make it easier to find SayHi on your device New startup and background graphics Post recording buttons look nicer Upside down device orientation is now supported for conversations to make it easier to share Patch for possible failure of speech output with certain languages under rare circumstances

Big changes with 1.2! GREATLY improved processing time Improved speech recognition accuracy Added support for 5 new languages! French German Italian Japanese Mandarin Chinese Added interactive tutorial Stability and performance improvements UI Adjustments Prepared for iOS 5

Detection of empty recordings Redesigned recording feedback and controls Text entry feature now uses language native buttons Updated tutorial Option to review the tutorial when an input error is detected Removed hold to talk functionality to simplify usage Speed and stability improvements Server revision support In addition to the client updates we are always making improvements to our server systems including improved translation accuracy and error correction.
Minor changes to hold to talk functionality
Better handling of server messages.
